metadata.name: Weird Uncle Official #1
metadata.description: I've had a letter from my uncle for years, he was an unbalanced and weird subject, I never gave him the importance he owed until one day he decided to digitize that letter to sell it in the metaverse as NFT, and that's how my torment began, it was divided into thousands and my eccentric uncle transferred his consciousness to an avatar in the metaverse, now he won't stop bothering me, his letter was divided into thousands of NFTs which hide secrets from the crazy old man, I need to hide all the NFTs and prevent the crazy cat from the one who became my uncle did not get them, please help me hide them in the metaverse ¡¡¡¡Please Help!!!
